====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# a [[string]] of [[one]] [[thousand]] [[coin]]s
#* {{zh-x|^楊 ^志 道：「祖上-留下 寶刀，要 賣 三-千 貫。」|Yang Zhi said: "This is a precious sword left by my ancestors; I will sell it for three '''thousand strings of cash'''."|ref=Shuihuzhuan}}
# to [[go through]]; to [[pierce]]
#* {{zh-x|自 始 合，而 矢 貫 余 手 及 肘，余 折 以 御，左-輪 朱-殷{yān}，豈 敢 言 病？|From the moment the troops clashed, arrows '''pierced''' my arm and elbow. I broke them off so as to drive the chariot. The left wheel has turned dark red with blood. Did I dare to speak of my wounds?|ref=Zuozhuan-D}}
#* {{zh-x|子曰：「參{Shēn} 乎！吾-道 一 以 貫 之 。」曾{Zēng}子 曰：「唯。」子 出。門人 問 曰：「何謂 也？」曾{Zēng}子 曰：「夫子 之 道，忠-恕 而已 矣。」|{{w|Confucius|The Master}} said, “Shen, a single thread '''runs through''' my doctrine.” {{w|Zengzi|Master Zeng}} said, “Yes.” The Master went out, and the other disciples asked, “What did he mean?” Master Zeng said, “The Master’s doctrine is nothing other than loyalty and empathy.”|ref=Lunyu}}
# one's [[native]] [[place]]
#* {{zh-x|他 岳丈 名 喚 ^封 ^肅，本-貫 ^大-如-州 人氏。|His father-in-law was a man named Feng Su, whose '''native place''' was Daruzhou.|ref=Hongloumeng}}
# {{lb|zh|sushi}} {{zh-classifier|[[sushi]]|t=}}

